query:
SELECT puzzle_id, Count(DISTINCT user_id) as count
                FROM VerifiedSpeedSolve
                WHERE blind = $1
                    AND uses_filters <= CASE
                            WHEN $2 THEN $3
                            ELSE puzzle_primary_filters
                        END
                    AND uses_macros <= CASE
                            WHEN $4 THEN $5
                            ELSE puzzle_primary_macros
                        END
                GROUP BY puzzle_id
                ORDER BY count DESC, puzzle_id;
